{{Han etyl}}
{{Han compound|一|刀|ls=ic|t2=sword}} – [[blade]]; tip of a blade. Original form of {{och-l|芒|[[awn]] (of cereal); [[tip]] (of blade)}}; later borrowed to mean “side”. Other theories regarding the origin of this character also exist.

It is unrelated to {{och-l|㫃|fluttering flag}}, from which characters like {{och-l|旗|flag}} and {{och-l|旅|troops}} are derived.

